PATENT NOTICE
================================================================================

The following innovations are patent pending and protected by intellectual
property law:

1. HYBRID POST-QUANTUM KEY ENCAPSULATION MECHANISM
   - Application: Turkey Patent Office (TPE)
   - Status: Patent Pending
   - Invention: X25519 + ML-KEM-1024 hybrid KEM with domain separation

2. BIDIRECTIONAL REPLAY PROTECTION SYSTEM
   - Application: Turkey Patent Office (TPE)
   - Status: Patent Pending
   - Invention: Prefix-based counter separation for replay detection

Patent applications are in progress. Use of these patented methods requires
written permission from the patent holder: Halil İbrahim Serdaroğlu.

