CRYPTOGRAPHIC NOTICE
================================================================================

This software implements cryptographic algorithms subject to export control
regulations in various jurisdictions. Users are responsible for compliance
with applicable export control laws.

The following cryptographic algorithms are implemented:
- ML-KEM-1024 (NIST FIPS 203) - Post-Quantum KEM
- X25519 (RFC 7748) - Elliptic Curve Diffie-Hellman
- Ed25519 (RFC 8032) - Digital Signatures
- XChaCha20-Poly1305 (RFC 7539) - Authenticated Encryption
- BLAKE2b - Cryptographic Hash Function
- Argon2 - Password Hashing

